item.title: About
item.description: As you might figured out, my name is Balazs Kreith and I am a software engineer by profession.

Objective Quality for WebRTC conferences Objective Quality is an indicator metric of the quality of WebRTC conferences. The metric is used to evaluate conferences at callstats.io. Blogpost: Objective Quality v3 MPRTP plugin for Gstreamer Multipath extension of Real-Time Protocol (MPRTP) makes real-time multimedia communication capable of transferring on multiple path. To realize it a Gstreamer plugin is developed capable of sending and receiving packets on multiple path. State: Active
